Class Sensor.SensorComparator

java.lang.Object
  nodes.Sensor.SensorComparator
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.Comparator<Sensor>
Enclosing class:
Sensor
public static final class Sensor.SensorComparator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator<Sensor>

A sorter for sensors that can sort sensors by various things. Other than the "SORT_BY_ID" and "SORT_NATURAL_ORDER" sort, the sorts VIOLATES(!) the natural sorting order for sensors.

Author:
Niels Thykier

SORT_BY_TURNS

public static final int SORT_BY_TURNS
Sort sensors by when their turn. If two sensors have a tie, the tie will be cleared by a single (unstored) re-roll.
